    </div>
    <div class="box-product">
      <img
        src="https://globo-toro.myshopify.com/cdn/shop/files/home10-banner-02.jpg"
        alt=""
        width="100%"
        height="100%"
      >
      <div class="content"><h2>BIKER JACKET WITH PADDED SHOULDER</h2></div>
      <div class="animation">&nbsp;</div>
    </div>
    <div class="box-product">
      <img
        src="https://globo-toro.myshopify.com/cdn/shop/files/home10-banner-03.jpg"
        alt=""
        width="100%"
        height="100%"
      >
      <div class="content"><h2>CONTRAST COAT</h2></div>
